---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<Layout title="TRT Evaluation" description="Lab-driven testosterone evaluation with honest, clinical assessment. Not a sales-driven TRT clinic. Telehealth across Florida.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-light to-bg py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">TRT Evaluation</span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-primary-dark mb-6">Lab-driven testosterone evaluation and care</h1>
        <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          A comprehensive, evaluation-first approach to testosterone care. We start with symptoms and labs — not a sales pitch. If TRT isn't right for you, we'll tell you.
        </p>
        <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-light text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-base font-semibold transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/25">
          Book a Visit
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Steps -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading eyebrow="Our Process" title="Evaluation before everything" subtitle="A structured, honest approach to testosterone care that starts with understanding your symptoms and labs." />
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3 mt-2">Symptom Evaluation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-light text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Structured review of fatigue, mood changes, libido, and concentration</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Full medical history and current medications assessment</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Open discussion before any decisions are made</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3 mt-2">Lab-Based Assessment</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-light text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Testosterone panel: total testosterone, free testosterone, SHBG</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Comprehensive bloodwork including CBC and metabolic panel</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Provider-led results review with clear explanation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3 mt-2">Monitoring & Adjustments</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-light text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Regular follow-up check-ins if TRT is appropriate</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Individualized dose adjustments based on labs and response</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-1">&#9679;</span> Periodic monitoring labs every 3&ndash;6 months</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Honest Approach -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-warm-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Our Philosophy</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-primary-dark mb-6">Honest evaluation, not a sales funnel</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Unlike many TRT clinics, we don't start with the assumption that you need testosterone. We start with your symptoms and your labs. If TRT isn't clinically appropriate, we'll be upfront about it and help you explore other options.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-warm-dark/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-dark text-sm mb-1">Labs first</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light text-xs leading-relaxed">Decisions are driven by your bloodwork, not assumptions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-warm-dark/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-dark text-sm mb-1">Honest conversation</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light text-xs leading-relaxed">We'll tell you if TRT isn't the right fit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-warm-dark/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-dark text-sm mb-1">Ongoing care</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light text-xs leading-relaxed">Not a one-visit clinic. We monitor and adjust over time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading eyebrow="Common Questions" title="What to know" />
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            Can TRT be managed via telehealth?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Yes. Symptom evaluation, lab ordering, results review, and ongoing management can all be handled effectively through telehealth visits.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            Do you accept insurance for TRT?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">No. MBS Medical is a cash-pay practice. This keeps your care simple, private, and free from insurance-driven limitations.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-primary-dark font-medium">
            What if I'm not a candidate for TRT?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-light group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">We'll be upfront about it. If your labs and symptoms don't support TRT, your provider will explain why and discuss alternative approaches to address your concerns.</div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-primary">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-4">Start with an evaluation</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10">Get a clear, lab-based picture of where you stand — no pressure, no sales pitch.</p>
      <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-primary-dark px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-base font-semibold hover:bg-warm-light transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
        Book a Visit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
